While I don't really want to, I'm looking to sell my T218 partial set. I just do not have the time to focus on completing it. I've uploaded images of the two key cards in the lot - not pretty and definitely a 1 as stated, but they are there. 

While I'd like to sell the entire lot, I'm also open to considering individual cards. Offers will be considered. I have estimated numerical grades and photos are available. If it is professionally graded, that is noted. List of cards available is below:
